  13:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time OCRef clear configuration
  14:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Timer remapping capabilities configuration
