  28:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                       ##### TIMER Extended features #####
  29:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  30:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   [..]
