 151:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                       ##### Timer Hall Sensor functions #####
 152:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
 153:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   [..]
 154:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     This section provides functions allowing to:
 155:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) Initialize and configure TIM HAL Sensor.
 156:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) De-initialize TIM HAL Sensor.
 157:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) Start the Hall Sensor Interface.
 158:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) Stop the Hall Sensor Interface.
 159:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) Start the Hall Sensor Interface and enable interrupts.
 160:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) Stop the Hall Sensor Interface and disable interrupts.
 161:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) Start the Hall Sensor Interface and enable DMA transfers.
 162:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (+) Stop the Hall Sensor Interface and disable DMA transfers.
 163:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c **** 
 164:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c **** @endverbatim
