 168:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief  Initializes the TIM Hall Sensor Interface and initialize the associated handle.
 169:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @note   When the timer instance is initialized in Hall Sensor Interface mode,
 170:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *         timer channels 1 and channel 2 are reserved and cannot be used for
 171:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *         other purpose.
 172:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  htim TIM Hall Sensor Interface handle
 173:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  sConfig TIM Hall Sensor configuration structure
 174:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL status
